content.rendered:
Play Dinogen Online : Action Game

An Action Game where you’ll be playing as dinosaurs or people, trying to defeat your enemies.

Controls :

Mouse – Shooting, WASD keys – Movement, SHIFT – Sprint, CTRL – Crouch, E – Interaction, R – Reload, Spacebar – Melee, G – Grenade, F – Use equipment, Q – Switch weapon, TAB – Scoreboard, Enter key – Chat
